title: I am looking for marriage details of my #greatgreatgrandparents & keep seeing references to it well after the fact.
content: MY GREAT-GREAT GRANDMOTHER'S PREMATURE DEATH appears to have greatly affected many in her community. Five years later, the forty fifth anniversary, it is noted again in the paper.  ajh
